<exercise id="fs-id1478280">
<problem id="fs-id2287454"><para id="fs-id2024704">Lactose is a disaccharide formed by the formation of a ________ bond between glucose and ________.</para>
<list id="fs-id1596510" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
